WEBVTT

00:04.003 --> 00:06.089
<i>The human brain is remarkable.</i>

00:06.173 --> 00:08.675
<i>For nine years
I thought I'd lost my watch</i>

00:08.759 --> 00:11.053
<i>cos I can't remember
which wrist it's on.</i>

00:11.136 --> 00:13.138
<i>And yet, after two weeks,</i>

00:13.222 --> 00:19.102
<i>the things that scared me at first,
catheters, chest tubes, IVs...</i>

00:19.186 --> 00:21.647
<i>Everything has started to click.</i>

